summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the dismissal of proceedings partaining to certain tracts or parcels of land situate between Bayview Street and Plum Street, from that certain condemnation proceeding for the laying off, extending and establishing of 26th Avenue South and other streets and avenues, as provided for by Ordinance No. 60444, being Cause No. 245115 of the Superior Court of the State of Washington for King County.
